data.description: All Brick Ranch Home With A 3-Car, Side-Entry Garage With New Garage Door, Upper & Lower Driveway & Is Beautifully Situated On A (1+) Acre Corner Lot. This Property Has A Swimming Pool & Pool House. Formal Living & Dining Room, Kitchen, Family Room With Fireplace, 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, and Large Laundry Room All On The Main Level. Screened Porch Off The Kitchen Overlooks The Pool & Fenced Back & Side Yard. Home is on public sewer.  There Is So Much Potential In This Home -- Come Add Your Personal Touch. Home Is Being Sold "As Is, Where Is". No HOA!
